{
  "stem": "11000.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I remember distinctly those people who had two left shoes or two right shoes, they had to find somebody else who had the opposite.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And luckily, you had two shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It turned out that later, this was a very important thing in life at camp, because if you had shoes that didn't fit or caused any infection and you were unable to walk straight, that was a reason-- you know, we didn't have any hospitals or-- or-- or medications-- that sometimes could have led to problems, and you-- and we had other selections in camp that you were not found to be qualified to go on.",
      "word_count": 76
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's number B, the letter B11668.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You never forget those.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After that, we were marched to a camp that's adjacent to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's called Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there I met a prisoner who had been there before, who was sent there before.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had been there for some time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a communication problem, because there were people from all countries.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Most of them where from the eastern countries.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, we had problems-- problems to communicate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this man who was Dutch, he said to me, he said, do you people really know where you are here?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, we're gonna work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They'll probably assign us to factories.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I really wasn't under the impression at that time that, since my father was sent to the other side, who was at the time maybe in his early 50's that he probably would get an assignment of a different kind of work.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, who was only, you know, in my teens, probably would be sent to the more physical work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I wasn't really so much concerned.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Eventually, I'd probably see him again.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
